    +-------------------------+
    |   loop until no chunks |
    +-------------------------+
             |
             v
   Agent reads chunk of 200 rows
             |
             v
   Agent reasons & cleans it
             |
             v
   Agent calls `document_learning_insights(notes=...)`
             |
             v
   Tool:
     - Logs markdown + JSON
     - Auto-embeds
     - Increments global chunk counter
             |
             v
     Agent can recall prior notes later using vector search
